title: Ben Carson says he was once held at gunpoint at a Baltimore Popeye's
text: Dr. Ben Carson, a Republican presidential candidate and retired Johns Hopkins Hospital neurosurgeon, said he once got the business end of a gun stuck in his ribs in a Popeye's restaurant in Baltimore.
